WEBVTT

00:00.075 --> 00:01.613
<i>Previously</i>
<i>on "Childhood's End"...</i>

00:01.734 --> 00:03.807
<i>At least 40 cities</i>
<i>around the world</i>

00:03.927 --> 00:05.894
<i>now have these vessels</i>
<i>hovering over them.</i>

00:05.929 --> 00:07.829
- My name is Karellen.
- Suffering will end.

00:07.864 --> 00:09.398
Injustice will end.

00:09.432 --> 00:10.732
<i>It's world peace.</i>

00:10.767 --> 00:12.601
<i>All hold hands and sing Kumbaya.</i>

00:12.635 --> 00:15.137
<i>This is an invasion.</i>

00:15.171 --> 00:16.271
Ahh!
My eyes!

00:16.306 --> 00:17.272
Why are you here?

00:17.307 --> 00:18.573
We need a messenger.

00:18.608 --> 00:20.175
<i>The birth rate is soaring.</i>

00:20.209 --> 00:23.145
<i>We have a world that we are</i>
<i>proud to bring children into.</i>

00:23.179 --> 00:25.347
<i>It's the golden age</i>
<i>of man, Utopia.</i>

00:25.381 --> 00:27.215
<i>Why did you make this room?</i>

00:27.250 --> 00:28.784
<i>Why did you send me Annabel?</i>

00:28.818 --> 00:31.920
<i>Because she is still the most</i>
<i>important thing in your life.</i>

00:31.955 --> 00:34.156
One day you'll understand
why I came back

00:34.190 --> 00:35.424
and why he built the room.

00:35.458 --> 00:36.491
Ricky?

00:36.526 --> 00:38.226
Karellen
is not letting you move on.

00:38.261 --> 00:39.895
Are you stealing
the Titan drives?

00:39.929 --> 00:40.929
Private research.

00:40.964 --> 00:42.264
<i>For 20 years, the Overlords</i>

00:42.298 --> 00:44.900
<i>have told us precisely nothing</i>
<i>about themselves.</i>

00:44.934 --> 00:46.001
I'm a guy
that likes to know stuff.

00:46.035 --> 00:47.869
It's Karellen.
He's back.

00:47.904 --> 00:49.638
Very good to see you, Ricky.

00:49.672 --> 00:52.341
He said that the Earth
has a new destiny.

00:54.310 --> 00:56.144
<i>Karellen said that there was</i>
<i>something in the fabric</i>

00:56.179 --> 00:57.746
<i>of the ship that poisoned me.</i>

00:57.780 --> 00:59.047
Help us!

00:59.082 --> 01:01.850
Karellen said that something
special was coming.

01:01.884 --> 01:03.585
Don't touch us.

01:04.721 --> 01:06.054
I take it you're the Greggsons.

01:06.089 --> 01:09.524
Our son Tommy is having
some behavioral issues.

01:11.995 --> 01:13.595
Tom just said
the strangest thing.

01:13.629 --> 01:14.596
- Jennifer.
- What?

01:14.630 --> 01:16.598
I know what to call the baby.

01:16.632 --> 01:19.334
We need to reclaim some of
what we had when we were kids.

01:19.369 --> 01:21.036
We're not moving to New Athens.

01:21.070 --> 01:22.471
It might be good for all of us.

01:22.505 --> 01:23.972
We need to add these people
to the guest list.

01:24.007 --> 01:25.674
This gentleman wants to fly me

01:25.708 --> 01:27.042
to South Africa
for a job interview.

01:27.076 --> 01:28.377
Your whole family's invited.

01:28.411 --> 01:30.379
- Milo Rodricks.
- Jake Greggson.

01:30.413 --> 01:31.947
- Here's my card.
- He's here.

01:31.981 --> 01:33.181
The supervisor for Earth.

01:33.216 --> 01:35.384
You're killing
scientific curiosity.

01:35.418 --> 01:38.653
Your scientific curiosity
would've destroyed you.

01:38.688 --> 01:40.856
The supervisor would like
to meet with you.

01:43.526 --> 01:45.694
We'll find a new voice
inside you.

01:47.597 --> 01:48.563
Tom!

01:48.598 --> 01:49.831
Jennifer, she's awake.

01:49.866 --> 01:52.434
No!

01:52.468 --> 01:54.169
So each symbol is a letter.

01:54.203 --> 01:55.303
This one is new.

01:55.338 --> 01:56.671
I recognize the pattern, Rachel.

02:00.276 --> 02:01.710
Jennifer.

02:01.830 --> 02:09.032
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny</font>
<font color="#ec14bd">www.addic7ed.com</font>

02:09.151 --> 02:11.186
Hey.

02:13.256 --> 02:14.689
Hi.

02:14.724 --> 02:16.124
Want to say hi to Mommy?

02:16.159 --> 02:17.759
Jennifer.

02:17.794 --> 02:20.662
Hey, Jennifer.

02:20.696 --> 02:22.064
Hello, pretty girl.

02:24.167 --> 02:25.700
Oh, hi.

